  "faqQ1": "How to use Maa AI Chat?",
  "faqA1": "Just type your question in the chat screen! Maa AI is always listening and ready to support you with pregnancy and baby care advice.",
  "faqQ2": "Is my health data safe and private?",
  "faqA2": "Absolutely! MaaCare uses secure InsForge PostgreSQL encryption for all logs. Your data is private, fully under your control, and never shared.",
  "faqQ3": "How do I track my baby's growth and vaccinations?",
  "faqA3": "Use the Child Growth or Vaccination Tracker from the home dashboard. Log height/weight or tick off vaccines to sync with our database.",
  "faqQ4": "What is the premium subscription?",
  "faqA4": "Super Mom Premium unlocks unlimited AI chats, priority consulting, and extra features for just ₹99/month.",
  "faqQ5": "How can I book a session with a doctor?",
  "faqA5": "Go to the Consult tab. Select a certified doctor, pick a date and slot, pay securely via Razorpay, and join the video call right from the app.",
  "faqQ6": "How does Sakhi AI differ from Maa AI?",
  "faqA6": "Sakhi AI is specially tuned for menstrual cycle tracking, ovulation, and PCOS guidance. Maa AI focuses on pregnancy and parenting.",
  "faqQ7": "What is the Symptom Checker risk tool?",
  "faqA7": "It uses AI models to analyze symptoms you input and flags potential health risks offline. Always consult a real doctor for medical decisions.",
  "faqQ8": "Can I request account deletion?",
  "faqA8": "Yes. Go to Settings, scroll to the bottom, and tap 'Request Data Deletion'. This permanently erases all your data."
